    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [300ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong> to the pan with the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and 2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
