    {
      "instruction": "<p>Set the <strong>harissa haddock stew</strong> and <strong>warmed ciabattas</strong> in the centre of the table, ready to share</p><p>Mix the<strong> natural yoghurt</strong> through the stew and top with the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>dill</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
